# Education Performance & Resource Allocation Dashboard

## Project Overview
Dashboard for analyzing student performance, attendance, resource allocation, and utilization using Power BI.

## Files Included
 Dashboard.jpeg
education_dataset.xlsx

## Tools Used
Excel / Power BI
GitHub

## Features
Attendance Analysis
Average Marks
Pass vs Fail Ratio
Resource Usage
Interactive Visualizations

